substring 1,2,3,4
---------
we can use a :(colon)
operator to access the substring
string_name[staring index : ending index]
eg : str="ABHI"
     str[:]    =ABHI
     str[0:3]  =ABH
     str[0:]   =ABHI
     str[:4]   =AHBI
     
